[Episode 33]

24
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:36,680
Who's that?

25
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:38,640
Ming Xin.

26
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:40,280
Who's this?

27
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:43,976
It really is him.

28
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:46,690
Why is he with Ming Yi and Ji Bozai?

29
00:01:46,790 --> 00:01:47,980
Where did they go?

30
00:01:48,230 --> 00:01:49,230
Yeah.

31
00:01:52,350 --> 00:01:54,130
I don't need your pity!

32
00:01:55,950 --> 00:01:59,460
I never thought that after a
lifetime of being jealous of you,

33
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:02,820
I wouldn't even die by
your hand in the end.

34
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,620
What's going on?

35
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:08,570
Ming Xin.

36
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:09,800
He's injured.

37
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,726
Isn't that Ming Xian's companion beast?

38
00:02:21,750 --> 00:02:22,750
- Yes.
- Yes.

39
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:32,080
I,

40
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:35,730
Ming Xin, Lord Chengyun
of Yaoguang Mountain

41
00:02:36,630 --> 00:02:38,380
and Ming Xian's younger brother,

42
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,570
can testify before you all.

43
00:02:41,590 --> 00:02:42,820
This woman

44
00:02:43,750 --> 00:02:47,820
is none other than Ming Xian of
Yaoguang Mountain, the one who caused

45
00:02:48,190 --> 00:02:49,336
your seven consecutive defeats!

46
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:49,976
What?

47
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,726
What? How could she be Ming Xian?

48
00:02:51,750 --> 00:02:52,256
Impossible!

49
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:53,660
She's clearly a fairy!

50
00:02:54,870 --> 00:02:55,536
Nonsense!

51
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,256
- Exactly.
- Yes.

52
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,776
How can he say such
nonsense with a straight face?

53
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:58,800
I don't believe him.

54
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:01,010
For the past 21 years,

55
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:06,290
she had used the Veil of
Illusion to disguise herself

56
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:08,340
as a male immortal,

57
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:11,890
taking the title of
Crown Prince for herself.

58
00:03:16,310 --> 00:03:18,730
The artifact in her hand, the Embers,

59
00:03:20,310 --> 00:03:21,940
was forged by Ming Xian

60
00:03:22,710 --> 00:03:24,170
and answers only to her.

61
00:03:25,190 --> 00:03:28,890
She also wears the spiritpact bell
of Ming Xian's companion beast,

62
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,820
the White Cat.

63
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:36,820
Is Fairy Ming Yi really Ming Xian?

64
00:03:37,590 --> 00:03:37,976
No,

65
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,446
it's impossible.

66
00:03:39,470 --> 00:03:41,380
She's a fairy. How could she be Ming Xian?

67
00:03:41,910 --> 00:03:43,830
But even Ming Xian's
own brother identifies her.

68
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:44,960
And the companion beast

69
00:03:45,030 --> 00:03:47,446
we just saw was indeed Ming Xian's cat.

70
00:03:47,470 --> 00:03:48,470
It can't be faked.

71
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:52,380
Ming Xian, do you dare deny it?

72
00:04:01,150 --> 00:04:05,450
Your identity will be
exposed sooner or later.

73
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:07,890
I don't believe

74
00:04:09,150 --> 00:04:10,410
that after all this,

75
00:04:11,190 --> 00:04:13,130
the Six Realms will
still have a place for you.

76
00:04:19,070 --> 00:04:22,100
The Crown Prince of Yaoguang Mountain

77
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:28,540
should have been me.

78
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:30,920
It should have

79
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:37,040
been me.

80
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,576
Could what he said be true?

81
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:52,730
Is it true?

82
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:53,980
It sounds true to me.

83
00:04:56,270 --> 00:04:57,366
There's no reason to make this up.

84
00:04:57,390 --> 00:05:00,100
- Get out!
- Get out!

85
00:05:00,750 --> 00:05:01,750
What are you doing?

86
00:05:02,510 --> 00:05:03,510
What are you doing?

87
00:05:03,630 --> 00:05:04,456
Calm down, everyone!

88
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:05,480
Step back!

89
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:06,810
Calm down, everyone!

90
00:05:06,870 --> 00:05:07,870
Back up!

91
00:05:08,070 --> 00:05:09,070
Do not come closer!

92
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,240
Stop!

93
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,480
Calm down!

94
00:05:13,310 --> 00:05:14,310
Step back!

95
00:05:14,830 --> 00:05:16,810
Stay calm! Step back!

96
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,410
Get out!

97
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,600
Back up!

98
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,020
Calm down, everyone!

99
00:05:21,270 --> 00:05:22,406
Get out of Shouhua Academy!

100
00:05:22,430 --> 00:05:24,730
- Get out!
- Get out!

101
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,700
Ming Yi is one of us here
in Shouhua Academy.

102
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:28,576
You cannot drive her out
just because you want to!

103
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,536
Ming Yi?

104
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,846
She's Ming Xian of Yaoguang Mountain!

105
00:05:30,870 --> 00:05:32,050
- Right!
- Right!

106
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:32,926
Everyone, please calm down.

107
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:33,980
Yes, she is Ming Xian,

108
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:36,246
but she's saved Jixing Abyss
from disaster more than once.

109
00:05:36,270 --> 00:05:38,100
Have you all forgotten that?

110
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:39,720
And every artifact

111
00:05:39,830 --> 00:05:41,136
used in this Qingyun Tournament

112
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:42,220
was forged by her.

113
00:05:42,870 --> 00:05:44,550
She has stood with us through every trial.

114
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:45,900
Why are you defending her?

115
00:05:46,190 --> 00:05:47,336
Why shouldn't I?

116
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,096
When the netherbeast army struck,

117
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:48,806
it was Master Ming Yi

118
00:05:48,830 --> 00:05:50,216
who protected the lives of Jixing Abyss!

119
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:52,046
She was once the Crown
Prince of Yaoguang Mountain.

120
00:05:52,070 --> 00:05:53,656
If you let her stay in Shouhua Academy,

121
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:55,336
aren't you afraid she'll
collude with the enemy

122
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:57,486
and bring ruin upon Jixing Abyss?

123
00:05:57,510 --> 00:05:59,290
That's nonsense! She would never do that!

124
00:05:59,510 --> 00:06:00,780
Enough talk!

125
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:01,776
Let's rush in

126
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:03,896
and drive that traitor out of Jixing Abyss!

127
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,340
Drive her out of Jixing Abyss!

128
00:06:13,940 --> 00:06:14,950
Calm down!

129
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:18,920
Get lost!

130
00:06:19,270 --> 00:06:20,270
Master.

131
00:06:20,750 --> 00:06:21,780
Calm down!

132
00:06:21,950 --> 00:06:22,950
Stop it!

133
00:06:23,830 --> 00:06:24,900
I am Ming Xian.

134
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:26,930
If anyone has grievances,

135
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,140
come at me.

136
00:06:28,190 --> 00:06:29,290
Ming Xian, you traitor!

137
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:30,536
Get out of Jixing Abyss!

138
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:32,100
Get out of Shouhua Academy!

139
00:06:32,430 --> 00:06:35,170
- Get out!
- Get out of Jixing Abyss!

140
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,730
- Get lost!
- Get lost!

141
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:40,700
Your Majesty, the news has
already spread across all Six Realms.

142
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:41,846
Fairy Ming Yi

143
00:06:41,870 --> 00:06:43,776
is none other than Ming Xian,
the one who caused Jixing Abyss

144
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,486
seven years of defeat and
the loss of the Blessed Rain.

145
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:47,370
Has Your Majesty been blinded by her deceit

146
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,610
to have allowed her to
join Shouhua Academy?

147
00:06:50,830 --> 00:06:53,170
Your Majesty, please seize
that traitor Ming Xian at once!

148
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:57,216
Yaoguang Mountain once hailed
that wretch as their Warrior God.

149
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:58,286
She built her own glory

150
00:06:58,310 --> 00:07:00,290
on the blood and tears Jixing Abyss offered

151
00:07:00,430 --> 00:07:01,780
to Yaoguang Mountain.

152
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,680
And now, she's even infiltrated our realm.

153
00:07:03,870 --> 00:07:05,250
She must have ulterior motives!

154
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,410
- Yes, Your Majesty.
- That's right, Your Majesty.

155
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:08,810
Your Majesty, we must
not let her go unpunished!

156
00:07:09,270 --> 00:07:11,390
Nor should we allow her to
remain in Shouhua Academy!

157
00:07:11,430 --> 00:07:13,140
We can't let her stay in Shouhua Academy!

158
00:07:13,310 --> 00:07:15,810
- Your Majesty, you owe us an answer!
- You owe us an answer!

159
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:16,700
- Your Majesty!
- Your Majesty!

160
00:07:16,750 --> 00:07:17,406
She must not be forgiven!

161
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:18,976
- Stop hesitating, Your Majesty.
- Your Majesty.

162
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:21,200
- Your Majesty, make your decision now!
- Your Majesty!

163
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,980
Give us justice!

164
00:07:23,630 --> 00:07:24,900
I am indeed Ming Xian,

165
00:07:25,630 --> 00:07:27,406
and it's true that I caused Jixing Abyss

166
00:07:27,430 --> 00:07:28,580
to lose for seven years.

167
00:07:29,070 --> 00:07:30,846
But back then, I belonged
to Yaoguang Mountain.

168
00:07:30,870 --> 00:07:32,336
There was nothing wrong

169
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:34,540
with fighting for them.

170
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:35,930
Still,

171
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:38,580
the hardships Jixing Abyss faces today

172
00:07:38,750 --> 00:07:39,900
are partly my doing,

173
00:07:40,070 --> 00:07:41,700
and I cannot just stand by.

174
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:43,120
So now,

175
00:07:43,390 --> 00:07:44,926
I wish to join

176
00:07:44,950 --> 00:07:46,750
the warrior ranks of
Shouhua Academy to fight

177
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:49,560
for the Blessed Rain that should
rightfully be shared with you.

178
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,606
Who would believe you?

179
00:07:50,630 --> 00:07:52,406
What right do you have
to be in Jixing Abyss?

180
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:54,806
Ming Xian would fight for Jixing Abyss?

181
00:07:54,830 --> 00:07:56,900
You traitor, you lying wretch!

182
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:57,950
No one will believe you!

183
00:07:58,070 --> 00:07:59,590
You made us lose seven years in a row,

184
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:00,976
and you dare to give this speech here?

185
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:01,776
Get out of Jixing Abyss!

186
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:04,610
- Get out of Jixing Abyss!
- Get out of Jixing Abyss!

187
00:08:04,830 --> 00:08:08,290
- Get out of Jixing Abyss!
- Get out of Jixing Abyss!

188
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,040
Everyone,

189
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:11,926
I know you won't believe me

190
00:08:11,950 --> 00:08:13,170
no matter what I say.

191
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:16,250
But there's one thing
you know as well as I do:

192
00:08:16,750 --> 00:08:18,410
right now, in Jixing Abyss,

193
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,976
no one else can rival the
warriors of Yaoguang Mountain.

194
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,000
Only I can.

195
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,370
Without me,

196
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:26,246
you will lose again, just as
you did in those seven years.

197
00:08:26,270 --> 00:08:27,100
With me,

198
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:28,490
you might still have a chance.

199
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:31,930
If I truly mean to fight for Jixing Abyss,

200
00:08:32,390 --> 00:08:33,846
then you'll have a chance to win,

201
00:08:33,870 --> 00:08:35,430
and it will be your only chance to win.

202
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,600
So today,

203
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,460
I set up this arena.

204
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,700
If anyone can defeat me,

205
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:44,940
I will never again ask to
join Shouhua Academy.

206
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,440
You have so many powerful artifacts.

207
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,296
How could we possibly beat you?

208
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,320
- Exactly!
- Exactly!

209
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:53,060
Right.

210
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:55,460
- It's impossible!
- Right!

211
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,060
I won't use any artifacts.

212
00:09:01,270 --> 00:09:02,270
Everyone,

213
00:09:02,390 --> 00:09:04,130
you've all seen what Ming Xian can do.

214
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:06,130
She's just trying to humiliate us.

215
00:09:06,550 --> 00:09:08,610
That's right. She's trying to humiliate us.

216
00:09:09,150 --> 00:09:10,420
This is unfair!

217
00:09:10,870 --> 00:09:12,630
Then I'll even fight
without using my hands.

218
00:09:13,770 --> 00:09:14,936
What is she trying to do?

219
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:16,820
What now? Even so,

220
00:09:16,910 --> 00:09:18,820
