547
00:29:50,680 --> 00:29:51,840
That's a good deal, isn't it?

548
00:29:56,880 --> 00:29:57,880
It's just a pity

549
00:29:59,720 --> 00:30:00,900
that what I promised her...

550
00:31:23,550 --> 00:31:24,570
Today is a fine day.

551
00:32:43,070 --> 00:32:44,070
You came.

552
