♪ If your world was once
an endless wasteland ♪

585
00:35:15,710 --> 00:35:21,940
♪ I'd tear myself apart to
fill the wounds inside you ♪

586
00:35:22,050 --> 00:35:26,420
♪ Even if this life is like a shooting star ♪

587
00:35:26,480 --> 00:35:29,630
♪ Brief only for the sake of meeting you ♪

588
00:35:29,710 --> 00:35:34,630
♪ In this fleeting life ♪

589
00:35:34,790 --> 00:35:42,790
♪ I'll still be your light ♪

590
00:35:57,070 --> 00:35:58,070
The rain has stopped.

591
00:36:10,230 --> 00:36:11,230
If only

592
00:36:11,880 --> 00:36:13,296
