606
00:39:43,960 --> 00:39:44,960
Your Lordship!

607
00:40:08,150 --> 00:40:09,150
Your Lordship.

608
00:40:14,710 --> 00:40:15,710
Buxiu.

609
00:40:16,590 --> 00:40:17,590
Your Lordship.

610
00:40:19,190 --> 00:40:22,900
I have already channeled my spiritual
power into the Sky-Swallowing Array.

611
00:40:23,760 --> 00:40:25,940
My primordial spirit is now linked to it.

612
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:28,010
