- Why you're here first!

643
00:42:09,000 --> 00:42:10,090
Why are you on your knees?

644
00:42:10,440 --> 00:42:12,280
Fairy Ming Yi, I beg
you, please save my lord!

645
00:42:13,510 --> 00:42:14,570
What happened to Ji Bozai?

646
00:42:14,710 --> 00:42:16,166
The Heavenly Grief in
him has flared up again.

647
00:42:16,190 --> 00:42:17,650
