662
00:43:29,670 --> 00:43:31,990
♪ Until it turns weak ♪

663
00:43:33,910 --> 00:43:36,670
♪ I deceive myself into
thinking that to love once ♪

664
00:43:36,710 --> 00:43:39,030
♪ Is enough ♪

665
00:43:40,350 --> 00:43:45,590
